node.accessibility_caption: Photo by 🐶 Maxine the Fluffy Corgi on July 26, 2021. May be an image of dog and text that says 'In 2019, Maxine had surgery to repair a shoulder tear and remove bone spurs in her forelimbs, which occurred as a result of elbow osteoarthritis, which she's had since she was a puppy. Unfortunately this is very common in short-legged dogs like Maxine.'.

Welcome to the Little Chonk Space Jam. Who wants to join the Chonk Squad? @Superchewer #Superchewer #ad

The ONLY subscription box we have for Maxine is the Superchewer box.  Every month we get a themed box with some incredible toys that are made for monster chewers like Maxine.  They’re thoughtfully designed and are the only toys that last in our house.  We can’t recommend it enough.  If you want to try the Superchewer box, click the link in our bio to get this Space Jam box and $84 of FREE toys.  Chew on, my chonky friends.
